long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Get ready for the animal matching game with different fun sections! You have limited number of moves, do your best maneuvers and have fun.

How To Play
Played with Mouse.

Animals Puzzle Game Features
✓ Stylized graphics
✓ 5+ Level
✓ Fun sounds
✓ Little particle
✓ Basic control

Finally, you can enjoy these game for free (and more requests will be added)! Animals Puzzle Game extension does not contain any hidden ads.
